title: Kris Jenner is in no rush to marry Corey Gamble | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share Asked what the pair do together, he said: 'We do everything...your mom has got a lot of energy.' Still strong: The couple has been making headlines for more than two years. Here they are in Venice, California earlier this month 'I feel like being with your mom is better than being with any chick my age or younger. I think we do more than you younger girls do ... We have more fun than Kylie [Jenner] with her guy life, I promise.' And Kim Kardashian West is thrilled her mother has found love again with Corey. She said: 'He's such a nice person, and it's just been so fun to see my mom happy... Mom has had such a hard year, and it's been refreshing to see her have a good time.' Kris previously quipped she has 'too much sex.' She said: 'I literally have too much sex. I'm exhausted.' 'I've realized I don't want to get married, but I really have a lot of fun with Corey, and I love being with him. He said, 'I don't want kids. I love you, and I feel that way about you.''
